      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is a true diamond in the rough, showing significant wear and needing some dedicated TLC to get back to its best. It represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for someone handy looking for a rewarding restoration project or a very affordable fixer-upper!",
